summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Percentage of individuals using internet, with a total of 18 data points.
Overall Percentage of individuals using internet has increased over the Year

Percentage of individuals using internet is rapidly increasing from 2000 to 2002, rapidly constant from 2002 to 2006, rapidly increasing from 2006 to 2007, roughly constant from 2007 to 2008, rapidly increasing from 2008 to 2011, and lastly gradually constant from 2011 to 2017.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2010 and 2011.
Max Percentage of individuals using internet about 43.83 was recorded at Year 2017
Min Percentage of individuals using internet about 1.44 was recorded at Year 2000
This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Percentage of individuals using internet, with a total of 18 data points. The chart has 2 significant trends.
The longest trend is slightly increasing which exists from 2000 to 2014.
Similarly, the next significant trend is extremely increasing which exists from 2014 to 2017.
